                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010415-126-defend1240 t18010415-126-punish708"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>,</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
